# env files (can opt-in for committing if needed)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
Update the env structure.

Create `.env.example` only. Do not create `.env.local` and do not add real secrets.

Use these variables:

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=

RESEND_API_KEY=
RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=
ADMIN_NOTIFICATION_EMAIL_1=
ADMIN_NOTIFICATION_EMAIL_2=

CONTRACT_HEADER_LOGO_URL=
CONTRACT_FOOTER_LEFT_IMAGE_URL=
CONTRACT_FOOTER_RIGHT_IMAGE_URL=

NEXT_PUBLIC_CONTRACT_HEADER_LOGO_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_CONTRACT_FOOTER_LEFT_IMAGE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_CONTRACT_FOOTER_RIGHT_IMAGE_URL=

APP_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

Also update README.md to explain that `.env.local` must be created locally and never committed.
